{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Product Detail","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"CeStore Web - ReactJS web app & React Native mobile app for e-commerce","meta_description":"React Native currently creates vibrant wave in mobile application development. “Write once, Run anywhere”, then you can effectively produce mobile app across all platforms including iOS & Android by one language with “Native effect”.","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"cestore-web","toc":null,"keywords":["cestore","cestore template","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<h2 id=\"product-detail\"><a href=\"#product-detail\" aria-label=\"product detail permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Product Detail</h2>\n<h6 id=\"components\"><a href=\"#components\" aria-label=\"components permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Components</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>Component to mange the view of the product detail</li>\n<li>File locate: theme/src/components/productDetails/index.js</li>\n</ul>\n<h6 id=\"code-snippets\"><a href=\"#code-snippets\" aria-label=\"code snippets permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code Snippets</h6>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;div&gt;\n  &lt;section id=&quot;product-detail&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;div className=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div className=&quot;gallery&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;Gallery images={product.images} /&gt;\n      &lt;/div&gt;\n\n      &lt;div className=&quot;product-info&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;h2&gt;{product.name}&lt;/h2&gt;\n        &lt;Price product={product} variant={selectedVariant} isAllOptionsSelected={isAllOptionsSelected} settings={settings} /&gt;\n\n        &lt;Options options={product.options} onChange={this.onOptionChange} /&gt;\n\n        &lt;div className=&quot;btn-wrap&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;AddToCartButton product={product} variant={selectedVariant} addCartItem={this.addToCart} isAllOptionsSelected={isAllOptionsSelected} addingCartItem={addingCartItem}/&gt;\n          &lt;a className=&quot;add-favorite&quot; onClick={this.likeProduct}&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;img&quot; src={this.state.liked ? &quot;/assets/images/cestore/ic_favorited.svg&quot; : &quot;/assets/images/cestore/ic_favorite.svg&quot;}/&gt;&lt;span&gt;Add To Favorites&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;/div&gt;\n      &lt;/div&gt;\n\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n  &lt;section id=&quot;product-content&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;div className=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;nav className=&quot;tab&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;ul&gt;\n          &lt;li&gt;&lt;a className={this.state.showDescription ? &quot;active&quot; : &quot;&quot;} onClick={()=&gt;this.setState({showDescription:true})}&gt;Description&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n          &lt;li&gt;&lt;a className={!this.state.showDescription ? &quot;active&quot; : &quot;&quot;} onClick={()=&gt;this.setState({showDescription:false})}&gt;Details&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\n        &lt;/ul&gt;\n      &lt;/nav&gt;\n      {this.state.showDescription &amp;&amp; &lt;Description description={product.description} /&gt;}\n      {!this.state.showDescription &amp;&amp; &lt;Attributes attributes={product.attributes} /&gt;}\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n\n  &lt;RelatedProducts\n    settings={settings}\n    addCartItem={this.addToCart}\n    ids={product.related_product_ids}\n    limit={10}\n  /&gt;\n\n  {themeSettings.show_viewed_products &amp;&amp;\n    &lt;ViewedProducts\n      settings={settings}\n      addCartItem={this.addToCart}\n      product={product}\n      limit={themeSettings.limit_viewed_products || 4}\n    /&gt;\n  }\n\n  {themeSettings.disqus_shortname &amp;&amp; themeSettings.disqus_shortname !== &#39;&#39; &amp;&amp;\n    &lt;section id=&quot;comments&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div className=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;Disqus\n          shortname={themeSettings.disqus_shortname}\n          identifier={product.id}\n          title={product.name}\n          url={product.url}\n        /&gt;\n      &lt;/div&gt;\n    &lt;/section&gt;\n  }\n\n  &lt;section id=&quot;subscribe&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;div className=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;h2&gt;Subscribe and Get 15% Off&lt;/h2&gt;\n        &lt;form&gt;\n            &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; placeholder=&quot;Your email&quot;/&gt;\n            &lt;a&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/assets/images/cestore/ic_send_mail.svg&quot; alt=&quot;img&quot;/&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\n        &lt;/form&gt;\n      &lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h6 id=\"screenshots\"><a href=\"#screenshots\" aria-label=\"screenshots permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Screenshots</h6>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/46b12/detail.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 194.86623282718728%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Detail\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/84055/detail.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/86a0e/detail.png 200w,\n/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/b67b1/detail.png 400w,\n/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/84055/detail.png 800w,\n/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/14bdf/detail.png 1200w,\n/static/bbac359352d151506d87a60a9dcdd83f/46b12/detail.png 1383w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"image-galleries\"><a href=\"#image-galleries\" aria-label=\"image galleries permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Image Galleries</h2>\n<h6 id=\"components-1\"><a href=\"#components-1\" aria-label=\"components 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Components</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>Mange the UI for the product detial galleries</li>\n<li>The thumnail position can be controlled from the admin site: <a href=\"http://localhost:3000/admin/products\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:3000/admin/products</a></li>\n<li>File locate: theme/src/components/productDetails/gallery.js</li>\n</ul>\n<h6 id=\"code-snippets-1\"><a href=\"#code-snippets-1\" aria-label=\"code snippets 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code Snippets</h6>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;Fragment&gt;\n  &lt;ImageGallery\n    items={imagesArray}\n    showThumbnails={showThumbnails}\n    onClick={this.openLightbox}\n    lazyLoad={true}\n    slideInterval={2000}\n    showNav={themeSettings.product_gallery_shownav === true}\n    showBullets={showThumbnails}\n    showPlayButton={false}\n    showFullscreenButton={false}\n    slideOnThumbnailHover={true}\n    thumbnailPosition={themeSettings.product_thumbnail_position}\n    onSlide={this.setPhotoIndex}\n  /&gt;\n  {lightboxIsOpen &amp;&amp;\n    &lt;Lightbox\n        reactModalStyle={{ overlay: { zIndex: 1099 } }}\n        mainSrc={originalImages[lightboxPhotoIndex]}\n        nextSrc={originalImages[(lightboxPhotoIndex + 1) % originalImages.length]}\n        prevSrc={originalImages[(lightboxPhotoIndex + originalImages.length - 1) % originalImages.length]}\n\n        onCloseRequest={this.closeLightbox}\n        onMovePrevRequest={() =&gt; this.setState({\n            lightboxPhotoIndex: (lightboxPhotoIndex + originalImages.length - 1) % originalImages.length,\n        })}\n        onMoveNextRequest={() =&gt; this.setState({\n            lightboxPhotoIndex: (lightboxPhotoIndex + 1) % originalImages.length,\n        })}\n    /&gt;\n  }\n&lt;/Fragment&gt;</code></pre></div>\n<h6 id=\"screenshots-1\"><a href=\"#screenshots-1\" aria-label=\"screenshots 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Screenshots</h6>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/046a785887c4d157e6b050493658f834/25800/gallery.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 112.67361111111111%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Detail Gallery\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/046a785887c4d157e6b050493658f834/84055/gallery.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/046a785887c4d157e6b050493658f834/86a0e/gallery.png 200w,\n/static/046a785887c4d157e6b050493658f834/b67b1/gallery.png 400w,\n/static/046a785887c4d157e6b050493658f834/84055/gallery.png 800w,\n/static/046a785887c4d157e6b050493658f834/25800/gallery.png 1152w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"comment-disqus\"><a href=\"#comment-disqus\" aria-label=\"comment disqus permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Comment Disqus</h2>\n<h6 id=\"components-2\"><a href=\"#components-2\" aria-label=\"components 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Components</h6>\n<ul>\n<li>In order to change the change the Disqus user, Go to Admin / Setting / Theme to change the <strong>DISQUS shortname</strong></li>\n<li>File locate: theme/src/components/productDetails/index.js and theme/src/components/comments/disqus.js</li>\n</ul>\n<h6 id=\"code-snippets-2\"><a href=\"#code-snippets-2\" aria-label=\"code snippets 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Code Snippets</h6>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{themeSettings.disqus_shortname &amp;&amp; themeSettings.disqus_shortname !== &#39;&#39; &amp;&amp;\n  &lt;section id=&quot;comments&quot;&gt;\n    &lt;div className=&quot;container&quot;&gt;\n      &lt;Disqus\n        shortname={themeSettings.disqus_shortname}\n        identifier={product.id}\n        title={product.name}\n        url={product.url}\n      /&gt;\n    &lt;/div&gt;\n  &lt;/section&gt;\n}</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import React from &#39;react&#39;\n\nconst DISQUS_CONFIG = [\n  &#39;shortname&#39;, &#39;identifier&#39;, &#39;title&#39;, &#39;url&#39;, &#39;category_id&#39;, &#39;onNewComment&#39;\n];\nlet __disqusAdded = false;\n\nfunction copyProps(context, props, prefix = &#39;&#39;) {\n  Object.keys(props).forEach((prop) =&gt; {\n    context[prefix + prop] = props[prop];\n  });\n\n  if (typeof props.onNewComment === &#39;function&#39;) {\n    context[prefix + &#39;config&#39;] = function config() {\n      this.callbacks.onNewComment = [\n        function handleNewComment(comment) {\n          props.onNewComment(comment);\n        }\n      ];\n    };\n  }\n}\n\nexport default class Disqus extends React.PureComponent {\n  constructor(props) {\n    super(props);\n  }\n\n  componentDidMount() {\n    this.loadDisqus();\n  }\n\n  componentDidUpdate() {\n    this.loadDisqus();\n  }\n\n  addDisqusScript() {\n    if (__disqusAdded) {\n      return;\n    }\n\n    const child = this.disqus = document.createElement(&#39;script&#39;);\n    const parent = document.getElementsByTagName(&#39;head&#39;)[0] ||\n                 document.getElementsByTagName(&#39;body&#39;)[0];\n\n    child.async = true;\n    child.type = &#39;text/javascript&#39;;\n    child.src = &#39;//&#39; + this.props.shortname + &#39;.disqus.com/embed.js&#39;;\n\n    parent.appendChild(child);\n    __disqusAdded = true;\n  }\n\n  loadDisqus() {\n    const props = {};\n\n    // Extract Disqus props that were supplied to this component\n    DISQUS_CONFIG.forEach((prop) =&gt; {\n      if (!!this.props[prop]) {\n        props[prop] = this.props[prop];\n      }\n    });\n\n    // Always set URL\n    if (!props.url || !props.url.length) {\n      props.url = window.location.href;\n    }\n\n    // If Disqus has already been added, reset it\n    if (typeof DISQUS !== &#39;undefined&#39;) {\n      DISQUS.reset({\n        reload: true,\n        config: function config() {\n          copyProps(this.page, props);\n\n          // Disqus needs hashbang URL, see https://help.disqus.com/customer/portal/articles/472107\n          this.page.url = this.page.url.replace(/#/, &#39;&#39;) + &#39;#!newthread&#39;;\n        }\n      });\n    } else { // Otherwise add Disqus to the page\n      copyProps(window, props, &#39;disqus_&#39;);\n      this.addDisqusScript();\n    }\n  }\n\n  render() {\n    return &lt;div id=&quot;disqus_thread&quot; /&gt;;\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h6 id=\"screenshots-2\"><a href=\"#screenshots-2\" aria-label=\"screenshots 2 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Screenshots</h6>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/99743366c903d3d541ca34989a188f43/dcb55/comments.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 47.18614718614719%; p